                                      "type": "text",
                                      "id": "SYpIM",
                                      "fill": "$text-secondary",
                                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                                      "width": "fill_container",
                                      "content": "Write an in-depth analysis of global AI regulatory frameworks, comparing approaches across major economic blocs. Focus on the EU AI Act, US Executive Order 14110, and China's layered regulatory system. Highlight the philosophical differences and practical implications for AI developers operating across jurisdictions.",
                                      "lineHeight": 1.5,
                                      "fontFamily": "$font-ui",
                                      "fontSize": 13,
                                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                                    }
                                  ]
                                }
                              ]
